HEADWORD: Sleighing
<hw>Sleigh"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of riding in
a sleigh.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of the snow or ice which admits of running
sleighs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sleight</ent>⟦br⟧
